{"tid":1990250,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人係心理變態﹐好鍾意睇人失敗既新聞?","createTime":"2020-04-26T14:06:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-27T09:03:02.000Z","uid":78243,"like":14,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"c57deef127382b0784d21497bc2cfda1b43a3167","tid":1990250,"uid":78243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T14:06:22.000Z","msg":"每次睇新聞見到人因為唔同事而自殺或者犯罪入獄﹐我都會忍唔住望多幾眼<br />\n我係一個失敗者﹐借住睇他人既失敗﹐而說服自己其實都唔算咁差同咁慘啫<br />\n跟住就會繼續hea 落去﹐唔願做出改變<br />\n有無人同我一樣都係失敗者同心理變態? 定只係得我一個會係咁?"},{"pid":"6cfd8b2435bf4a34396f660ffa30a04012d2473c","tid":1990250,"uid":210165,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T14:09:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"01332c1b4d9753d3a0b4d756194c7b6c3ddf244b","tid":1990250,"uid":5649,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T14:11:03.000Z","msg":"正常人睇到非手足被捕/自殺應該都有一絲絲快感"},{"pid":"27a4462bbbb050f2cf011d23ec290631cebf2335","tid":1990250,"uid":20809,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T14:15:56.000Z","msg":"竟然有d咁真實既說話聽到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cac5160d4a4bcdb6b4924bf9c19cf99b4cee2033","tid":1990250,"uid":286155,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T14:36:55.000Z","msg":"果啲人成世未失敗過，一跌就起唔返身<br />\n樓主我地應該慶幸自己係loser，衰到貼地嘅人係唔會驚跌低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23682a64b534003ef15ebce35a60ea6d72120ae5","tid":1990250,"uid":78243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cac5160d4a4bcdb6b4924bf9c19cf99b4cee2033","tid":1990250,"uid":286155,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T14:36:55.000Z","msg":"果啲人成世未失敗過，一跌就起唔返身<br />\n樓主我地應該慶幸自己係loser，衰到貼地嘅人係唔會驚跌低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T14:39:34.000Z","msg":"又俾你講得通<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />可以繼續打飛機"},{"pid":"7263c3f96742a8a9191ce88c44c471db9a6167d6","ti